The following organizations may maintain a list consisting of trained and equipped emergency response, public health, and medical personnel:
Local units formed under Section 300hh of Title 42 of the United States Code;
Disaster relief organizations;
Licensing boards;
National or regional associations of licensing boards of health practitioners;
Health facilities that provide comprehensive inpatient and outpatient health-care services, including a tertiary care and teaching hospital; or
Governmental entities.
